    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Store the verification key and Issuer public key. Called once after deploy.\\n\\n`issuer_pub_key` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Ed25519 public key (32 bytes) of the trusted KYC issuer.\\nThe Issuer signs Poseidon commitments during KYC (Option A architecture).\\nHardcode the real key before mainnet deployment.",
